    "They argued that tree structures like ASTs might fall short in this regard.",
    "To address this issue, Phan et al.",
    "adopted CFGs and applied GCN to extract expressive features.",
    "By leveraging CFGs, they were able to capture intricate program dependencies and interactions more effectively.",
    "The GCN allows the generation of expressive features that incorporate both local and global information from the program's control flow."
